    <div class="ifde-standard__inner">

                <div class="section__content bg-feature__content ifde-standard__content">
                  <h2  class="section_title bg-feature__title">
        
            Start Your Journey
      
  
    </h2>


<div  class="bg-feature__ctas">
            <div  class="bg-feature__cta bg-feature__cta--one">
        
            <a href="/admission/undergraduate-admission" target="">Undergraduate Admission </a>
      
  
    </div>

      <div  class="bg-feature__cta bg-feature__cta--two">
        
            <a href="/admission/graduate-admission" target="">Graduate Admission </a>
      
  
    </div>


  </div>
    
            
      
  


        </div>
        
    </div>

</div>

            <div class="gen-block-twocol paragraph paragraph--type-gen-block-2-column paragraph--view-mode-default ifde-twocol clearfix">
    

    <div class="ifde-twocol__inner">

                <div class="gen-block-twocol__header ifde-twocol__header">
                
      <h2 class="section__title gen-block-twocol__title">Welcome to Soka! </h2>
      
  

      <div  class="section__intro gen-block-twocol__intro">
        
            <p>“Creating Value” is the core of Soka University&#8217;s academic philosophy. It begins with the unique and dynamic nature of the Soka learning community. You will meet, live, and learn with people from more than 40 nations. You will get an education that prepares you for a career and offers experiences that employers nationwide and worldwide are seeking. You will discover new worlds at Soka, from modern technology&nbsp;to ancient wisdom. You will accomplish things you never imagined.</p>
      
  
    </div>


        </div>
        
                    <div class="gen-block-twocol__columns ifde-twocol__content">
            
            <div class="field field--name-field-gen-block-col-1 field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__item"><div class="gen-block">
    

        <div class="gen-block__media media">
            
            <div class="image">
  
      
                <picture>
                  <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/gen_block/public/images/2023-07/IMG_7623.jpeg?h=ba3afe5f&amp;itok=XIAJ-ej_ 1x" media="(min-width: 1025px)" type="image/jpeg" width="400" height="281"/>
              <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/gen_block/public/images/2023-07/IMG_7623.jpeg?h=ba3afe5f&amp;itok=XIAJ-ej_ 1x" media="(min-width: 700px)" type="image/jpeg" width="400" height="281"/>
              <source srcset="/sites/default/files/styles/generic_block_sm/public/images/2023-07/IMG_7623.jpeg?h=ba3afe5f&amp;itok=EdhTUUv9 1x" type="image/jpeg" width="700" height="490"/>
