  </picture>


      
  


</div>


      
  


    </div>
    
        <div class="gen-block__caption caption">
              <h3  class="gen-block__title">
        
            <a href="/admission/graduate-admission" target="">Graduate Admission</a>
      
  
    </h3>

      <div  class="gen-block__subtitle">
        
            Master of Arts in Education Leadership &amp; Societal Change
      
  
    </div>

      <div  class="gen-block__body">
        
            <p>At Soka we believe that education is the road not just to a career but to happiness, fulfillment, and a more peaceful and sustainable world. Your degree will prepare you for a contributive life of meaning and change.</p>
      
  
    </div>


    </div>
    
</div>
</div>
      
            </div>
        
        
    </div>

