        <span class='accordion__icon'></span>
    </button>

    <div class="accordion__content">
            
            <p>Our team of admission counselors is here to assist you through every step of your college search and admission process.&nbsp;We regularly travel to various college fairs across the country.</p>

<p>Find out who your admission counselor is and see if we are&nbsp;visiting your area in the near future: <a href="https://admissions.soka.edu/portal/meet-your-counselor" target="_blank">Undergraduate</a>, <a href="https://admissions.soka.edu/portal/meet-your-grad-couns" target="_blank">Graduate</a></p>
      
  


